  [ 16] getlocal 0 .............................. <room>
  [ 18] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [ 19] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <room, 0>
  [ 21] objcall 826 ............................. room.setSelectOnPress(0)
  [ 24] ret
end

